data.description: WATERFRONT VIEW!! Immaculate custom home with upper & lower decks. Featuring: Combo living w/dining. Open concept kitchen with Butcher Block Island, built-in Ice Maker. 6 bedrooms, 4 bathrooms. Main floor: Master bedroom with bath, 2 bedrooms w/putnam sinks. Full bathroom for your guests. 2nd floor: living room with 2 lofts looking into the room, 3 bedrooms & 2 bathrooms. Over the 4 car garage is an Apartment/Mancave or Airbnb income property with 2 bedrooms, 1 bathroom and a deck. Garage is climate controlled. Outside features: Plenty of parking spaces with concrete circle drive. Firepit. 2 boat slips w/electric, water and stereo system. 2 Jet ski lifts. A MUST SEE!
